Class RandomBaselineSMEAnalysis

    • org.openimaj.experiment.evaluation.cluster.analyser.RandomBaselineSMEAnalysis

    AnalysisResult

    public class RandomBaselineSMEAnalysis
extends Object
implements AnalysisResult
    Results of applying a RandomBaselineSMEAnalysis to evaluate clustering. These metrics are taken from the Introduction to Information Retrieval. Sina Samangooei (ss@ecs.soton.ac.uk)

    • Field Detail

      • purity

        public RandomBaselineClusterAnalysis<PurityAnalysis> purity
        A measure of how pure each cluster is. P = 1/N Sigma_k max_j | w_k AND c_j |

        Count the true classes of all the elements in a class, make a count of the largest group from each cluster, divide by number of elements in all clusters.

        High means: most of the clusters had a high number of a single class Low means: most of the clusters had a roughly equal spread of all the classes
